name: Keep Moving On
description:
Recently I have a lot things to decide, one of them about my artworks on HEN.

From now, I decided to drop only a simple animated or still image artworks on HEN. It's hard things for me to decide but I must do it because I want to drop more artworks with complex animation exclusively 1/1 edition not on HEN, I want to give my appreciation for anyone who want to collect it since complex animation takes more time & effort from me.

I know it will be more obstacles ahead, but I will KEEP MOVING ON just like Sam on Death Stranding. So that's the idea behind this artwork.

LFG! WAGMI! WML! Cheers!
